==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hastily
<hw>Has"ti*ly</hw> <pr>(h⟦amac⟧s"t⟦icr⟧*l⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<ety>[From <er>Hasty</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In haste; with speed
or quickness; speedily; nimbly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Without due reflection; precipitately;
rashly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>We <qex>hastily</qex> engaged in the war.</q>
<rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Passionately; impatiently.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hastiness</ent>⟦br⟧
